# Architecture Diagram

This folder contains architecture diagrams for the Serverless Contact Form Application project.

## Architecture Overview

The solution uses a serverless AWS architecture consisting of:

* Amazon Route 53
* Amazon CloudFront
* Amazon S3
* Amazon API Gateway
* AWS Lambda
* Amazon DynamoDB

## Request Flow

User → Route 53 → CloudFront → S3 Static Website → API Gateway → Lambda → DynamoDB

## Key Benefits

* Fully serverless architecture
* High availability
* Automatic scaling
* Low operational overhead
* Cost-efficient design

